{"tid":31333,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人童年回憶係去椰林閣食西餐","createTime":"2016-12-09T15:21:31.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-11T09:45:41.000Z","uid":32932,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"07c83a6a62283c9894794322cee69097c8d46077","tid":31333,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T15:21:31.000Z","msg":"細個嗰陣去椰林閣食晚餐覺得好高級好開心<br />\n個湯有酥皮㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家椰林閣執晒未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c376baa083fff8a8f78ce4bd08d2c088e93c4857","tid":31333,"uid":27359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T15:26:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc2a0cc6dfa668f7a3343cd3d28d85581f05bec9","tid":31333,"uid":11977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T15:31:42.000Z","msg":"細個老母帶食下午茶鋸扒幾抵屌"},{"pid":"7c222d125ed27f03f13a3a11bbea3c4e20254512","tid":31333,"uid":45188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T15:32:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>細個嗰陣去椰林閣食晚餐覺得好高級好開心<br />\n個湯有酥皮㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家椰林閣執晒未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仲有呀，但已經變晒貴版茶記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c18cccde6feab3648e034127d638b90ca090a220","tid":31333,"uid":6640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T15:36:55.000Z","msg":"已經變左童年回憶"},{"pid":"f1c7c7a4aed8025bd68768b3487dc900f8c65deb","tid":31333,"uid":61560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T15:41:58.000Z","msg":"agger<br />\n個格局幾高級咁又有羅宋湯又剩<br />\n以前好似四條友先廿舊水"},{"pid":"318cb36b1458ffb1d3facde37fedc81e7304e3b9","tid":31333,"uid":61560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T15:42:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>agger<br />\n個格局幾高級咁又有羅宋湯又剩<br />\n以前好似四條友先廿舊水</blockquote><br />\n自膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />兩舊水"},{"pid":"5fc86ff8ffd270eedad012cc5bc7c62de9883074","tid":31333,"uid":51924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T15:43:50.000Z","msg":"上菜慢(試過等左成個鐘) 野又難食<br />\n消失係應該"},{"pid":"52f37961fd855a75dddb92c86bd5668bfd864133","tid":31333,"uid":51344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T15:45:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>agger<br />\n個格局幾高級咁又有羅宋湯又剩<br />\n以前好似四條友先廿舊水</blockquote><br />\n對唔住，我笑撚左廿舊水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過椰林閣係堅抵食既"},{"pid":"5539849b31e0230d31f1c870b5bdd2a40647554d","tid":31333,"uid":43804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T15:46:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>細個嗰陣去椰林閣食晚餐覺得好高級好開心<br />\n個湯有酥皮㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家椰林閣執晒未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仲有呀，但已經變晒<span style=\"color: maroon;\">貴版茶記</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nagger<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32f33dd9c46d2ff7568be333103727cf3cfbb5bb","tid":31333,"uid":53261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T15:47:12.000Z","msg":"中學食我記得先廿四定廿六蚊"},{"pid":"d07412bcc893da32369e289978a7885f693f2104","tid":31333,"uid":2258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T15:49:19.000Z","msg":"最記得係食通粉有蔥<br />\n個味真係好怪好唔夾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1355b66f14f9af2305b8757c73895e9de219ba4","tid":31333,"uid":54010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T15:49:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>細個嗰陣去椰林閣食晚餐覺得好高級好開心<br />\n個湯有酥皮㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家椰林閣執晒未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n細個成日食 <br />\n記得聖誕都會同屋企人係個到食<br />\n但愈大愈貴 水準又差左<br />\n上年屋企樓下個間都執埋"},{"pid":"d52ea1c258bb48f03ed6a412f77eeef164915761","tid":31333,"uid":9906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T15:51:08.000Z","msg":"中學成日去，有段時間$25學生餐<br />\n有飯 有湯 有凍飲同餐包<br />\n都應該有十年前"},{"pid":"8554fc831cbc15e68f3e5c685d97b9b174690afe","tid":31333,"uid":45431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T15:56:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中學成日去，有段時間$25學生餐<br />\n有飯 有湯 有凍飲同餐包<br />\n都應該有十年前</blockquote><br />\n係，中學有少閒錢就會去食佢既學生餐，我記得係三十蚊左右，對於我黎講好撚貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2317f9a1d38df01d38e55768ddc03f55094dba1a","tid":31333,"uid":1749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T16:05:04.000Z","msg":"以家學生餐做緊41<br />\nSo far 都食得落ok 既"},{"pid":"a8e2abfe7a00f45785ffb443f68018192dd93f31","tid":31333,"uid":5328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T16:45:42.000Z","msg":"以前每個禮拜六、日都去食下午茶，樓下個間執粒之後依家都仲未搵到取代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 30幾蚊炒焗飯意粉大大碟。學生時代午餐又成日去鋸扒，好懷念<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc2a78dc4b08b6791a84bf6e0d4a01eb7f841358","tid":31333,"uid":33878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T16:47:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">係去超人餐廳食</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ea579a7b107a3a5232f4c9321ec2596907ed8f1","tid":31333,"uid":16846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T17:40:28.000Z","msg":"暑假老母帶落去食早餐，有餐包餐湯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"096a3e3bebfb3ce5c405862cef9fcf6d3da6b8fd","tid":31333,"uid":33787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T17:42:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9ae956d6dabe07340b7fb4d8112906ffdccc273d","tid":31333,"uid":33787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T17:43:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ac8c26fbc6804fbb2dc0a8bf9de880a0302392a4","tid":31333,"uid":12618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T00:47:10.000Z","msg":"普通雞扒意粉餐咁<br />\n夾個意粉加個扒搞掂啦<br />\n我等左成八個字都未到<br />\n本身想叫人催下<br />\n屌你無人理我<br />\n當我叫到個人黎時我話唔等要埋單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又難食 四五十蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cc5fffdc6d1767f0b54803a7784294569137bd7","tid":31333,"uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T00:47:50.000Z","msg":"d waitress西到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56392c89dce24ec957ff9ef3e0ad70377e200135","tid":31333,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T00:48:40.000Z","msg":"執咗變大快活<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />細個未入過去，多數食南風閣"},{"pid":"5956fbe14127ee5e803fb04fd9891568230235c3","tid":31333,"uid":31015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T01:10:05.000Z","msg":"觀塘仲有間 野食一般 但坐得舒服"}]}